response.original_title: Rebels with a Cause: The Story of the American Football League
response.overview: Chronciling the story of the American Football League from its founding in 1960 to its merger with the National Football League in 1966. Included is footage from some of the early A.F.L. games as well as the first four Super Bowls.
response.title: Rebels with a Cause: The Story of the American Football League
